                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020217-23-defend288 t18020217-23-punish122"></join>
               confined three months in Newgate
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18020217-23-punish123" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020217-23-punish123" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020217-23-punish123" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020217-23-defend288 t18020217-23-punish123"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Chambre.</p>
